{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7531ddaafc","title":"中央文化革命小组给昆明军区的电报","origin":"原载云南八·二三《风展红旗》编《毛主席无限关怀云南人民——中央和中央首长对云南无产阶级文化大革命的指示(内部资料)》，1968年4月","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"178972c04b","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":26,"articleId":"7531ddaafc"}],"tags":[{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"88958321be","name":"云南文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"728eaa90ea","type":"title","text":"中央文化革命小组给昆明军区的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7531ddaafc"},{"id":"90321bc5e6","type":"appellation","text":"昆明军区、云南军区并告八·二三和炮兵团的同志们：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7531ddaafc"},{"id":"72933b92fa","type":"paragraph","text":"据报，最近昆明武斗严重，八·二三和砲兵团双方都向人民解放军夺枪，并互相开枪射击。我们向你们提出以下意见：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7531ddaafc"},{"id":"b02e5bce10","type":"paragraph","text":"一、双方绝对禁止开枪；","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7531ddaafc"},{"id":"bd38475a7a","type":"paragraph","text":"二、双方都不许冲击军事领导机关；","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7531ddaafc"},{"id":"bff57aa0a6","type":"paragraph","text":"三、人民解放军一切武器装备物资，任何团体与个人都不得侵犯与抢夺，双方都应在“拥军爱民”的口号下正确对待人民解放军；","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7531ddaafc"},{"id":"f7a62510a4","type":"paragraph","text":"四、双方的争执，应在中央既定方针下，议商解决，—定要坚决制止武斗。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7531ddaafc"},{"id":"6ef12d29b4","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央文化革命小组一九六七年八月二十六日","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7531ddaafc"},{"id":"e831060508","type":"appellation","text":"(原载云南八·二三《风展红旗》编《毛主席无限关怀云南人民——中央和中央首长对云南无产阶级文化大革命的指示(内部资料)》，1968年4月。)","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7531ddaafc"}],"page":{"id":"e77004ccea","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7531ddaafc","start":0,"end":